[*] --> OnHold
OnHold --> Cancelled : review
Cancelled --> Pending : reject
Cancelled : entry / log shelf
Pending --> Closed : process
Closed --> Completed : confirm
OnHold --> Completed : revert
Completed --> [*]
@enduml